    <briefdescription>
<para>Time-stepping solver for articulated-body dynamics. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Wraps Featherstone forward dynamics and advances generalized state using semi-implicit integration. Quaternion state components are normalized after integration for free/ball joints. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
